Pil two directory of default data.

This directory as used for the variable $HOME and some plugins... on tmp dir
All data of the installed app data are here.

Games, Apps, Etc data are here, you can explore with File Manager from Zii to Multi-Arch_Pil

Libs can be installed here, manually, by packs of libs, Example: /pil/root/libs/libc6.so with the app Pil_Libs_Installer

Vars used here:
HOME=/pil/root

